[{"id":"VH978887","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH978884.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following is a correct expression for the magnetic force per unit length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction F over L\"><math alttext=\"the fraction F over L\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> exerted on the conductor and indicates the correct direction?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH978887_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"prose style:1\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a long, straight conductor that carries a current i directed out of the page. The conductor is contained in a uniform magnetic field B, which is directed to the right. A point labeled P is a horizontal distance r to the left of the conductor.\" height=\"102\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH978884.g01.png\" width=\"220\" /></div>\n\n<p class=\"passage_para\">A long, straight conductor is carrying a current <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I\"><math alttext=\"I\" overflow=\"scroll\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> that is directed out of the page. The conductor is in a uniform magnetic field of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" overflow=\"scroll\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> that is directed to the right, as shown. Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is located a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r\"><math alttext=\"r\" overflow=\"scroll\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to the left of the wire.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I B\"><math alttext=\"I B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>; toward the top of the page</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I B\"><math alttext=\"I B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>; toward the bottom of the page</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I B\"><math alttext=\"I B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>; toward the right</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"I B\"><math alttext=\"I B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>; toward the left</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0\"><math alttext=\"0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>; the direction is undefined</p>"],"answer":0}]